ğŸ’¾ Step 3: Instance Storage Options
1. EBS â€“ Elastic Block Storage
Persistent storage

Continues even if the instance is stopped

2. EC2 Instance Store (Volume)
Also called DAS (Direct Attached Storage)

Temporary â€“ If the instance is stopped, the storage is lost

âš ï¸ If your EC2 instance is terminated or stopped, Instance Store volumes are deleted by default.

